  "text": "Minimal important change (MIC) for NPRS-NP was identified with reference to the patient reported score of GROC-NP to differentiate the group that improved and that did not, at three levels of meaningful change as described above. Sensitivity and specificity values were also recorded. We hypothesized that NPRS-NP would be sensitive to change with MIC value between 1.1 and 3.5 as reported in the literature [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
